a:5:{s:5:"title";s:46:"Salesmate adds cover pages to quote templates";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:506:"<p>Salesmate introduced cover pages for quote templates, allowing teams to place an introduction and proposal context ahead of the pricing section.</p>
<p>Where to find it: Quotes → Templates → Cover Page.</p>
<p>Use cases: brief proposal summary, deliverables, timelines, “next steps” section, and other pre-pricing context.</p>
<p>Read full update here: <a href="https://www.salesmate.io/blog/january-2026-release-notes/">https://www.salesmate.io/blog/january-2026-release-notes/</a></p>
